.TH man 1 "3 Nov 2021" "1.0" simple_shell man page"

.SH NAME
simple_shell \- a simple Unix command Interpreter.

.SH SYNOPSIS
simple_shell [options] [command_string | File]

.SH DESCRIPTIONS
Simple_shell is a command line interpreter that reads input from the stdinput and it interprets them and executes them.

Simple_shell is inteded to be a replica of sh

.SH OPTIONS
Simple_shell takes no options But can run command with options.
Example of those commands
1. ls -la 
2. rmdir --ignore-on-failure

.SH SEE ALSO
man sh

.SH BUGS
 still in construction but so far no identified Bugs. If so will be updated.

